{"tid":832673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球前25大製藥市值2.7兆美元 嬌生蟬聯第一 中企首次進榜","createTime":"2018-09-23T03:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-23T15:11:44.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfb9489e256ec433cd0df624b95ce2107803434","tid":832673,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T03:03:27.000Z","msg":"國際製藥大廠的名聲耳熟能詳，但是，如果以市值為計算基準，排名會是如何？根據GlobalData最新的製藥市場分析報告，今年第二季底全球前25大製藥公司市值，與第一季相較，仍以嬌生居首，值得注意的是，中國的江蘇恆瑞首次進榜。<br />\n<br />\n該研究機構統計，這25大製藥公司截至上半年的總市值為2.7兆美元，其中，北美的公司有13家，市值1.5兆美元。而排名中比較值得注意的是，嬌生依舊名列第一，而中國則第一次有藥廠進入榜單，也就是中國醫藥股股王江蘇恆瑞。嬌生的股價第三季持續上漲，目前最新市值是3809億美元，至於江蘇恆瑞，第三季股價呈下跌趨勢，目前市值約2187億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n此外，若是以第二季相較於第一季的市值比較，25強平均增加1.1%，而個別公司中，則以默克美國、拜耳、葛蘭素史克、禮來、CSL和Shire的成長達到兩位數百分比。相對的，施貴寶和Celgene減少超過10%。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.genetinfo.com/investment/featured/item/20120.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.genetinfo.com%2Finvestment%2Ffeatured%2Fitem%2F20120.html&d=REILfn9PG8J42kYIDykZ0LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=20e5ba6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.genetinfo.com/investment/featured/item/20120.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5403712666/641\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_bt%2F0%2F5403712666%2F641&h=feb4c0ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hpcismart.com/images/website/ManChemNews/DIR_77/F_63941.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hpcismart.com%2Fimages%2Fwebsite%2FManChemNews%2FDIR_77%2FF_63941.jpg&h=cd65a18a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"810c79b49d3d0b6dcafac0eb8e58abe41847d8a6","tid":832673,"uid":75521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T15:11:44.000Z","msg":"勁"}]}